    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >麦卡的冒险者们：全新《流淌的欲念》 DLC 等你来玩！包含新职业、新玩法、新故事，可玩性up up！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新职业 - 傀儡师</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《流淌的欲念》是“因狄斯的谎言”系列首个<strong>独立的玩法章节</strong>，傀儡师们能通过魔铜为媒介提高自身力量，操纵生者的意志，掌握死者的灵魂。通过招募随从，傀儡师能够操控魔物和亡灵为自己而战。冒险中仍旧以DBG的卡组构筑为核心，可以根据自己流派构筑去选择合适的随从搭配，通过充分发挥随从的特性来取得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/a713cffd7e0f7fc4557578d8610badb5.poster.avif?t=1728974063\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/a713cffd7e0f7fc4557578d8610badb5.webm?t=1728974063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/a713cffd7e0f7fc4557578d8610badb5.mp4?t=1728974063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新玩法 - 随从机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >傀儡师可在旅途中招募随从，或在战斗中使用卡牌召唤亡灵。随从的意图每回合都会触发：进可输出破敌，退可以身防卫，还有多种特殊技能可以触发，释放最大潜能：使用“发动”技能在一回合内多次触发随从的战斗意图，用“烙印”为随从锁定攻击目标，“献祭”随从获得丰厚的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/daa22ad2fddc90e34312908dffc99df6.poster.avif?t=1728974063\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/daa22ad2fddc90e34312908dffc99df6.webm?t=1728974063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097790/extras/daa22ad2fddc90e34312908dffc99df6.mp4?t=1728974063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深入麦卡大陆的暗面</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣铜修隐会是隐秘在瑞帕里、灰岩交界处三不管地带的神秘组织。阵营大殿内供奉了一块品质罕见的魔铜，并以此作为基础研究魔铜秘术、救治信徒的病痛。与其他利用魔铜大力发展工业的组织不同，圣铜修隐会认为魔铜是因狄斯赐予人世间的一味良药。有一天，修隐会的教主消失不见，魔铜也不知所踪，傀儡师们踏上冒险，寻找失踪的教主和魔铜......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DLC内容概览</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新“傀儡师”职业和 3 个新角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新随从机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 个随从选项，各有所长</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 多张全新的职业专属卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 种新怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随从事件和傀儡师冒险故事</p></li></ul>",
